#: lib/bookshelf_settings.lua:148
msgid ""
"Tokens are placeholders that get replaced with live data when the book "
"detail view or status line renders.\n"
"\n"
"  %title — %book_pct\n"
"  → Dune — 36%\n"
"\n"
"Wrap content in [if:foo]…[/if] to show it only when the token has a value. "
"Add [else]…[/if] for a fallback.\n"
"\n"
"  [if:series]Book %series_num of %series_name[/if]\n"
"  [if:batt<20]LOW %batt[/if]"
msgstr ""
"Los tokens son marcadores que se sustituyen por datos en vivo al mostrar la "
"vista de detalle del libro o la línea de estado.\n"
"\n"
"  %title — %book_pct\n"
"  → Dune — 36%\n"
"\n"
"Envuelva contenido con [if:foo]…[/if] para mostrarlo solo cuando el token "
"tenga valor. Añada [else]…[/if] para una alternativa.\n"
"\n"
"  [if:series]Libro %series_num de %series_name[/if]\n"
"  [if:batt<20]BAJA %batt[/if]"

